folder: Broome Street & Elizabeth Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
355-361 Broome Street, at, adjoining, and west of the S.W. corner of Elizabeth Street. Third building on the right is the Roman Catholic Church of San Salvatore. The view also shows 133-131 Elizabeth Street. The second house to the left is a one-story frame.

About 1914.

(2)

The same, showing a farther view on Elizabeth Street.

May 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
